               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <note/>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1923" notAfter="1924"/>
                     <note>
                     According to <ref target="#coloph1"/>, the manuscript was written in the year of mercy <date calendar="ethiopian">1916 CE</date>, i.e. 
                     <date>1923-24 AD</date>, during the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5226haylase">Rās Tafari Ḫayla Śǝllāse</persName>.  
                     The manuscript was donated by the same king <persName role="bequeather" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5226haylase">Ḫayla Śǝllāse</persName> to pope 
                     <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7895PiusXI">Pius XI</persName> on the occasion of a solemn audience held on <date>20 June 1924</date>.
                     </note>
                  </origin>
